\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1/2 pound good bittersweet chocolate such as Lindt\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 pound good {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/chocolate/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 semisweet chocolate}} such as Ghiradelli\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 cup {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cream/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 heavy cream}}\
